        "label": "ORG"
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_010_108_000036",
    "sentence": "一日，節度使召璘，適有獻雙鯉者，戲曰：「君卜此魚何時得食？」",
    "entities": [
      {
        "text": "一日",
        "label": "TME"
      },
      {
        "text": "節度使",
        "label": "TITLE"
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_010_108_000037",
    "sentence": "璘良久答曰：「公與仆不出今日，有不測禍，奚暇食魚？」",
    "entities": [
      {
        "text": "今日",
        "label": "TME"
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_010_108_000038",
    "sentence": "亟命烹之。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_010_108_000039",
    "sentence": "未及食，寇至，俱遇害。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_010_108_000040",
    "sentence": "耶律敵魯，字撒不碗。",
