      },
      {
        "text": "撒不碗",
        "label": "PER"
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_010_108_000041",
    "sentence": "其先本五院之族，始置宮分，隸焉。",
    "entities": [
      {
        "text": "五院",
        "label": "ORG"
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_010_108_000042",
    "sentence": "敵魯精於醫，察形色即知病原。",
    "entities": [
      {
        "text": "敵魯",
        "label": "PER"
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_010_108_000043",
    "sentence": "雖不診候，有十全功。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_010_108_000044",
    "sentence": "統和初，為大丞相韓德讓所薦，官至節度使。",
    "entities": [
      {
